    <item>
      <title>受制裁的俄罗斯天然气厂首次向亚洲运送货物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/sanctioned-russian-gas-plant-sends-cargo-to-asia-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受到制裁的俄罗斯液化天然气出口设施首次向亚洲发送了一批货物，莫斯科方面正在继续寻找愿意购买这种燃料并规避美国限制的客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/sanctioned-russian-gas-plant-sends-cargo-to-asia-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 02:32:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党指责拜登团队就阿富汗撤军问题撒谎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/republicans-accuse-biden-team-of-lying-about-afghanistan-pullout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党议员在一份报告中指责拜登政府向美国人撒谎，并在2021年阿富汗撤军期间牺牲了美军士兵的安全，并试图在总统大选前牵连副总统卡马拉·哈里斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/republicans-accuse-biden-team-of-lying-about-afghanistan-pullout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 23:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前劳工部长警告称 PFI 纠纷威胁英国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/former-labour-minister-warns-pfi-disputes-threaten-uk-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位前工党卫生大臣警告称，除非英国政府为本届议会任期内到期的150多份遗留私人融资计划合同建立解决框架，否则英国政府将很难通过私营部门建设新医院和其他主要基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/former-labour-minister-warns-pfi-disputes-threaten-uk-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒默警告政府可能在 9 月 30 日截止日期前关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/schumer-warns-of-government-shutdown-ahead-of-sept-30-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默强调避免 9 月 30 日政府关门的重要性，因为议员们将在 8 月份休会后返回华盛顿，而美国大选将于 11 月举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/schumer-warns-of-government-shutdown-ahead-of-sept-30-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 22:13:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
